 high\nmass-transfer rate favors the hypothesis that hydrodynamical lift is the cause\nof the disk tilt.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2012 16:44:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
