y reach beyond 5 AU only under favorable\nconditions. However, within the explored space of disk parameters, only a small\nfraction - less than a few per cent - of the models predict that the interior\nplanet reaches beyond 4 AU.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2012 18:26:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 15:26:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
