ne the extinction energies of several\nLaue spots of the studied sample. The energies filtered-out by the diamond\ncrystal are obtained by measuring its Laue pattern with an other 2D detector,\nat each rotation step. This article demonstrates the feasibility of the method,\nand its validation through the measurement of a known lattice parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2012 07:58:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2012 20:18:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2012 17:06:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-19"}
